DOC.brief_summary: A study to describe and evaluate patient characteristics and clinical outcomes in Subjects with diagnosed Non Small Lung Cell Cancer in Sweden, Norway and Denmark.
DOC.brief_title: Long-term Epidemiological Follow-up of Non-small Cell Lung Cancer in Scandinavia
DOC.criteria: Patients with a histologically confirmed diagnosis of NSCLC (squamous, adenocarcinoma, not otherwise specified NSCLC [NSCLC NOS]) identified in the Cancer registers Age under 18 years at time of diagnosis
